SELECT product.Code as Product_Code, product.Revision as Product_Revision, product.Description as Product_Desc, bom.EffectiveBeginDate as BOM_EffectiveBeginDate, bom.EffectiveEndDate as BOM_EffectiveEndDate, bom.LeadTimeOffset as BOM_LeadTimeOffset, bom.Quantity as BOM_Quantity, bom.Shrink as BOM_Shrink, bom.EffectiveEndDay as BOM_EffectiveEndDay, bom.EffectiveBeginDay as BOM_EffectiveBeginDay, bom.Alternative as BOM_Alternative, bom.Line as BOM_Line, party.Code AS Party_Code, party.Name as Party_Name, party.Address as Party_Address, routing.Step as Routing_Step, vendoritem.VendorItem + '; ' + vendoritem.VendorItemRevision as VendorItem_VendorItem, um.Code as UM_Code, product.ProductID
FROM ITM_BOM bom LEFT JOIN ITM_Routing routing ON bom.RoutingID = routing.RoutingID LEFT JOIN ITM_Product product ON bom.ProductID = product.ProductID LEFT JOIN MST_Party party ON product.PrimaryVendorID = party.PartyID LEFT JOIN PO_ItemVendorReference vendoritem ON vendoritem.ProductID = product.ProductID AND vendoritem.PartyID = party.PartyID LEFT JOIN MST_UnitOfMeasure um ON product.StockUMID = um.UnitOfMeasureID

SELECT routing.Step as Routing_Step, case routing.Type when 0 then 'In' when 1 then 'Out' end as Routing_Type, routing.MachineSetupTime as Routing_MachineSetupTime, routing.MachineRunTime as Routing_MachineRunTime, routing.Machines as Routing_Machines, routing.LaborRunTime as Routing_LaborRunTime, routing.LaborSetupTime as Routing_LaborSetupTime, routing.CrewSize as Routing_CrewSize, routing.SetupQuantity as Routing_SetupQuantity, routing.StudyTime as Routing_StudyTime, routing.MoveTime as Routing_MoveTime, routing.EffectEndDate as Routing_EffectEndDate, routing.OSVarLT as Routing_OSVarLT, routing.OSFixLT as Routing_OSFixLT, routing.EffectBeginDate as Routing_EffectBeginDate, routing.OSOverlapPercent as Routing_OSOverlapPercent, routing.OSOverlapQty as Routing_OSOverlapQty, routing.OSScheduleSeq as Routing_OSScheduleSeq, routing.OSCost as Routing_OSCost,
case when routing.OverlapPercent is not null then 'Overlap Percent: ' + Convert( varchar(30), FLOOR(routing.OverlapPercent)) + '%' when routing.OverlapQty is not null then 'OverlapQty: ' + Convert(varchar(30), FLOOR(routing.OverlapQty)) when routing.ScheduleSeq is not null then 'Parallel: ' + Convert(varchar(30), FLOOR(routing.ScheduleSeq)) else 'Linear' end as Routing_ScheduleType,
routing.VarLT as Routing_VarLT, routing.FixLT as Routing_FixLT, routing.RunQuantity as Routing_RunQuantity, routing.Pacer as Routing_Pacer, routingStatus.Code as RoutingStatus_Code, wc.Code AS WorkCenter_Code, wc.Name AS WorkCenter_Name, func.Code AS Func_Code, laborCC.Code AS LaborCC_Code, machineCC.Code AS MachineCC_Code, party.Name AS Party_Name, party.Code AS Party_Code,routing.ProductID
FROM ITM_Routing routing LEFT JOIN MST_WorkCenter wc ON routing.WorkCenterID = wc.WorkCenterID LEFT JOIN MST_Function func ON routing.FunctionID = func.FunctionID LEFT JOIN ITM_RoutingStatus routingStatus ON routing.RoutingStatusID = routingStatus.RoutingStatusID LEFT JOIN ITM_CostCenter laborCC ON routing.LaborCostCenterID = laborCC.CostCenterID LEFT JOIN ITM_CostCenter machineCC ON routing.MachineCostCenterID = machineCC.CostCenterID LEFT JOIN MST_Party party ON routing.PartyID = party.PartyID
